                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 1r: ለዛቲ᎓ መጽሐፍ᎓ ዘአጽሐፋ᎓ አቤቶ᎓ ተክለ᎓ እግዚእ᎓ በእንተ᎓ ሕይወተ᎓ ነፍሱ᎓ ለወልደ᎓ ሚካኤል᎓ ወለብእሲቱ᎓ ሰበነ᎓ ጊዮርጊስ᎓ ወለደቂቁ᎓ ፀዳለ᎓ ማርያም᎓ ጸበለ᎓ ጊዮርጊስ᎓ ወወሀባ᎓ ለታቦተ᎓ ኪዳነ᎓ ምሕረት᎓ ደብረ᎓ ገነት᎓ ...</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 1r: The one who had this book written and who donated it to the tabot of Däbrä Gännät Kidanä Mǝḥrät is ˀabeto Täklä ˀƎgziˀ, for the sake of the life of the soul of Wäldä Mikaˀel and his wife Säbänä Giyorgis and his children Ḍädalä Maryam, Ṣäbälä Giyorgis … </q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 19v: ወሀሎ᎓ ፩ብእሲ᎓ ገባራ[sic]᎓ ወኮነ᎓ ያፈቅራ᎓ ለእግዚእትነ᎓ ማርያም᎓… </q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 19v: There was a man … that loved our Lady Mary … </q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
